，徽标和Otoreitamako个人资料已更改。" class="wp-image-98650"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：官方网站 © 2023 Aogiri High School / viviON, inc.</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>针对这一事件，该集团宣布在咨询其法律顾问后，正在考虑提起刑事指控。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="ja" dir="ltr"> 【暂停接受礼品的通知】<br>前几天，发生了一件GPS发射器被藏在送给会员的礼物中的事件。管理层正在咨询我们的法律顾问，并考虑对青桐高中的活动提出刑事指控。我们谨通知您，我们将继续停止接受礼物。</p> — 青桐高中教职员室 [官方] (@AogiriHS) <a href="https://twitter.com/AogiriHS/status/1755109132451881245?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 2 月 7 日</a></blockquote><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="5GIBw4evXr"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/aogiri-high-school-vtuber-chiyoura-chiyomi-suffered-a-traumatic-accident-but-was-not-fatally-injured/">VTuber Chomi Chiyoura 所在的青桐高中宣布，她的“创伤性事故”没有生命危险</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“青桐高中宣布，VTuber Chiyoura Chomi 的‘外伤事故’没有生命危险” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/aogiri-high-school-vtuber-chiyoura-chiyomi-suffered-a-traumatic-accident-but-was-not-fatally-injured/embed/#?secret=xgZRn90cWs#?secret=5GIBw4evXr" data-secret="5GIBw4evXr" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="KFP04DXtJI"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/aogiri-high-school-ranked-2nd-in-total-views-among-the-official-youtube-channels-of-vtuber-agencies-and-groups/">青桐高中在VTuber办公室/团体官方YouTube频道上获得总观看次数第二名</a></b