" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dokibird_youtube_channel_february_6_2024.png" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dokibird_youtube_channel_february_6_2024.png" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dokibird_youtube_channel_february_6_2024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-114173"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> Dokibird（截至2024年2月6日18:40）</figcaption></figure><p></p><p> 2月5日，NIJISANJI EN的运营公司ANYCOLOR对据称是Dokibird的表演者/声音模特的Seren Ryugetsu发出了投诉，称“<em>多次违反合同并在SNS上发布误导性虚假信息”。 &#39;据宣布，由于他的行为，合同将被终止</em>。</p><p>之后，Dokibird在他的X（Twitter）账户上宣布，他将于2月8日10:00开始进行“回归直播”。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="h7HQ59UIfu"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-terminates-nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-due-to-repeated-contract-violations-and-misrepresentations-on-sns/">ANYCOLOR公司NIJISANJI EN（新）VTuber Selen Tatsuki的合同被取消</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ANYCOLOR 取消了 NIJISANJI EN（新）所属 VTuber Selen Tatsuki 的合同” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-terminates-nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-due-to-repeated-contract-violations-and-misrepresentations-on-sns/embed/#?secret=jNvyzbketd#?secret=h7HQ59UIfu" data-secret="h7HQ59UIfu" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="17rE96r04p"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/alleged-actor-of-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-dokibird-to-return-streaming-on-february-8/">据称是VTuber Selen Tatsuki的表演者/声优模特的人将于2月8日进行“回归分配”</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTu